_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-357_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-358_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-359_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-360_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-362_">Aromatherapy massage with lavender oil</span></h4><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-evcjhq dAUdgU pf-363_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-346950c5--Massage-hands_1200x.jpg?v=1606852168" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-346950c5--Massage-hands.jpg?v=1606852168 1536w" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-364_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-366_">Lavender oil is a great choice for aromatherapy massage, as it helps to promote relaxation and stress relief. It‚Äôs also known for its anti-inflammatory and analgesic properties, which can help to relieve pain in the body.<br><br>Before it can be used in massage, lavender essential oil needs to be combined with a carrier oil, such as jojoba oil or sweet almond oil. You can also experiment by blending other essential oils with your lavender oil to maximise the benefits, glean other benefits, or simply because you have a favourite delicious scent!</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-528c" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-367_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-368_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-369_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-370_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-371_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-372_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-373_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-374_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-375_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-376_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-378_">Topical application of lavender oil</span></h4><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-evcjhq dAUdgU pf-379_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-1012c950--Oilonhands_1200x.jpg?v=1606851589" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-1012c950--Oilonhands.jpg?v=1606851589 1536w" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-380_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-382_">Lavender essential oil can also be applied topically to the skin. It is often used to treat <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3612440/" target="_self">wounds and burns</a> and can also be added to a bathtub or footbath. You can also use it in a compress or add it to a cream or lotion.<br><br>When lavender oil is applied topically, it should be diluted with a carrier oil, such as sweet almond oil or jojoba oil.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e993" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-383_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-384_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-385_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-386_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-387_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-388_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-389_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-390_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-391_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-392_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-394_">Pillow mist with lavender oil</span></h4><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-evcjhq dAUdgU pf-395_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/7c5a3545-1638981600001_1200x.jpg?v=1638981603" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/7c5a3545-1638981600001.jpg?v=1638981603 1536w" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-396_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-398_">If you‚Äôre looking for a way to enjoy the relaxing properties of lavender essential oil while you sleep, you can try making a lavender pillow mist. Simply add a few drops of lavender oil to distilled water and spritz it on your pillows before bed. The floral scent will help to calm and relax your mind while you drift off to a more peaceful, regenerative sleep.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-eb64" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-399_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-400_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-401_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-402_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-403_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-404_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-406_">Lavender essential oil research</span></h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-bilyIR cCHonK pf-407_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-evcjhq dAUdgU pf-408_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pexelsannashvets5682668-1646129162177_1200x.jpg?v=1646129165" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pexelsannashvets5682668-1646129162177.jpg?v=1646129165 1536w" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-dFtzxp VWXPf pf-409_">Photo by <strong><a href="https://www.pexels.com/@shvetsa?utm_content=attributionCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=pexels">Anna Shvets</a></strong> from <strong><a href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/person-in-white-dress-shirt-holding-clear-glass-bottle-5682668/?utm_content=attributionCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=pexels">Pexels</a></strong></div><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-410_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-412_">Due to lavender essential oil's popularity, there has been a lot of research conducted on the oil over the years. This is great news for those who rely on lavender oil for its therapeutic benefits, as it has been shown to be effective in many different areas.Let's take a look at some of the key studies that have been conducted to explore the benefits and use of lavender essential oil.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-ee09" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-413_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-414_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-415_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-416_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-417_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-418_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-419_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-420_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-421_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-422_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-424_">Lavender and the nervous system - 2013</span></h4><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-425_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-427_">This study, which was published in the journal Evidence-Based Complementary and Alternative Medicine, looked at the effects of lavender oil on the <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3612440/" target="_self">nervous system</a>. The researchers found that lavender oil had a significant effect on anxiety and stress levels.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-8ae6" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-428_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-429_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-430_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-431_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-432_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-433_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-434_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-435_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-436_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-437_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-439_">Lavender and sleep - 2015</span></h4><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-440_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-442_">A study published in the Journal of Alternative Complementary Medicine looked at the effects of lavender oil on <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4505755/" target="_self">sleep quality</a>. The researchers found that lavender oil was able to improve sleep quality in people with insomnia and also had a sedative effect.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-efc8" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-443_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-444_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-445_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-446_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-447_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-448_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-449_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-450_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-451_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-452_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-454_">Lavender and pain relief - 2016</span></h4><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-455_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-457_">A study in 2016 investigated the effects of lavender essential oil on <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27863613/" target="_self">pain cause by osteoarthritis</a> of the knee. The researchers found that aromatherapy massage with lavender essential oil was able to effectively reduce pain levels in people with chronic pain.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-143e" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-458_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-459_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-460_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-461_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-462_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-463_ pf-r pf-c-cm" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-464_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-465_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-466_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-467_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-469_">Lavender and wound healing - 2016</span></h4><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-470_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-472_">Another study in 2016 set out to explore the effects of applying lavender essential oil to <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4880962/" target="_self">wounds</a>. A solution of lavender oil was applied on alternating days for 14 days. It was discovered that the essential oil helped to increase the production of collagen, helping the wounds to heal faster.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-49f6" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-473_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-474_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-475_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-476_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-477_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-478_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-480_">Side effects of lavender essential oil</span></h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-bilyIR cCHonK pf-481_"><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-482_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-484_">Like any other substance, lavender essential oil can cause side effects when used incorrectly.<br><br>Some of the potential side effects of lavender oil include:</span></p></div><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-FNXRL lgZllt pf-485_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jWUzzU hBMhiW pf-486_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-488_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Headache: </span>Lavender oil can sometimes cause headaches when used in aromatherapy. This is usually because it is strong and needs to be diluted before use.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jWUzzU hBMhiW pf-489_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-491_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Skin irritation: </span>Lavender oil can cause skin irritation when applied topically to the skin. It is important to dilute lavender oil before using it in this way.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jWUzzU hBMhiW pf-492_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-494_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Drowsiness:</span> Lavender oil can sometimes cause drowsiness when used in aromatherapy. If you are driving, operating heavy machinery or in situations where you need to be alert, it is best to avoid using lavender oil.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-jWUzzU hBMhiW pf-495_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-497_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Allergic reaction:</span> Some people may experience an allergic reaction to lavender oil. If you experience any adverse effects after using lavender oil, stop use immediately and consult a doctor.</span></li></ul><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-498_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-500_">If you experience side effects of lavender oil, you should stop using it immediately. If the side effect is serious or doesn‚Äôt go away, it's important to seek medical advice as soon as possible.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-864e" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bQtKYq fbyRgD pf-501_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jHkVzv dyVEVs"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-502_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-503_"><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-504_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-505_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-506_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-508_">Contraindications of lavender essential oil</span></h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-bilyIR cCHonK pf-509_"><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-510_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-512_">Out of all the essential oils on the market, lavender is one of the most well known as well as one of the most researched essential oils. This is partly due to its popularity, along with its wide range of benefits.
